OL,3,CTrial of alleged Lockerbie bombmaker
OL,4,Ccould face four month delay
OL,6,FThe trial of a man accused of building
OL,7,Fthe bomb which destroyed Pan Am Flight
OL,8,F103 over the town of Lockerbie in the
OL,9,Fsouth of Scotland could face a delay
OL,10,Fof up to four months.
OL,12,FAll 259 passengers and crew onboard
OL,13,FPan Am Flight 103 and 11 people on the
OL,14,Fground were killed when the plane
OL,15,Fexploded above the town, in what
OL,16,Fremains Britain's deadliest terrorist
OL,17,Fatrocity.
