OL,3,CTrial of alleged Lockerbie bombmaker
OL,4,Ccould face four month delay
OL,6,FAbu Agila Masud who is alleged to have
OL,7,Fhelped make the bomb, was set to go on
OL,8,Ftrial in Washington DC in May 2025
OL,9,Ffacing three charges, which he denies.
OL,11,FBut a notification sent by the US
OL,12,FDepartment of Justice to relatives of
OL,13,Fvictims, seen by ITV News, suggests
OL,14,Fthat this could now face a delay, as
OL,15,FMasud receives treatment for an
OL,16,Fundisclosed health condition. As such,
OL,17,Fthe start of the trial could be pushed
OL,18,Fback between thirty and one hundred
OL,19,Fand twenty days.
