OL,3,CTrial of alleged Lockerbie bombmaker
OL,4,Ccould face four month delay
OL,6,FThe news comes ahead of the 36th
OL,7,Fanniversary of the attack, which is to
OL,8,Fbe marked with commemorative events in
OL,9,FLockerbie on Saturday.
OL,11,FThe founder and CEO of the Pan Am
OL,12,FFlight 103 Lockerbie Legacy
OL,13,FFoundation, Victoria Cummock, said:
OL,14,F"It's very difficult, we have raised
OL,15,Fhopes.
OL,17,F"We've been waiting for the better
OL,18,Fpart of a lifetime, you know 36 years
OL,19,Fis a lifetime.
