OL,6,F"But we have no say in any of it so we
OL,7,Fjust have to keep pushing as we have
OL,8,Fdone for the past 36 years."
OL,10,FHer husband, John, was among those who
OL,11,Fdied when the plane exploded on 21
OL,12,FDecember 1988.
OL,14,F"He was a loving husband and father,
OL,15,Fhe was also very proud of his Scottish
OL,16,Fheritage," she remembered.
OL,18,F"He loved his family, he was very
OL,19,Factive in local community charities,
OL,20,Fand taken suddenly and far too soon."
