OL,3,CTrial of alleged Lockerbie bombmaker
OL,4,Ccould face four month delay
OL,6,FScotland's Lord Advocate Dorothy Bain
OL,7,FKC said: "The bombing of Pan Am 103
OL,8,Fover Lockerbie was the darkest of days
OL,9,Fbut the dignity of the hundreds of
OL,10,Ffamilies so dreadfully affected has
OL,11,Falways shone as a point of light
OL,12,Fguiding the pursuit of justice.
OL,14,F"Scotland's prosecutors and police,
OL,15,Fworking with counterparts in the
OL,16,FUnited States have remained steadfast
OL,17,Fin our commitment to uncovering the
OL,18,Ftruth and holding those responsible
OL,19,Faccountable."
