OL,3,CTrial of alleged Lockerbie bombmaker
OL,4,Ccould face four month delay
OL,6,FFormer Libyan intelligence officer
OL,7,FAbdelbaset al-Megrahi is the only man
OL,8,Fconvicted in relation to the bombing
OL,9,Fafter being found guilty of 270 counts
OL,10,Fof murder by a panel of three Scottish
OL,11,Fjudges, sitting at a special court in
OL,12,Fthe Hague in 2001.
OL,14,FHe was sent to prison in Scotland but
OL,15,Fwas controversially granted
OL,16,Fcompassionate release in 2009 after
OL,17,Fbeing diagnosed with terminal cancer,
OL,18,Freturning home to Libya where he died
OL,19,Fin 2012.
